UNIX / LINUX:
============
UNIX/LINUX is an operationg system . By using operating system (OS) users or applications

commuinicate with hardware components

Two types of softwares:
=====================
1.system software
2.Application software

1.system software:
===================
By using system software we commuinicate with hardware devices
Eg: OS

2.Application software:
========================

By using application software we can perform some business things
Eg: python,java,.net....

UNIX OS:
========
UNIX os is freeware and open source
GUI and CUI 
multi user operating system

